Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.91,0:00:04.58,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,小哥 別傻站在那啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.58,0:00:05.53,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,菲魯特？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.53,0:00:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你居然是同年級的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.36,0:00:09.57,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,蛤？這不是當然的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:12.04,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}居然和這種小孩子是同級生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:14.04,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}真是可怕的異世界現實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.24,0:00:17.74,Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}{\c&H6E3C42&}Re:{\c&H6E48B4&}小{\c&H317FB6&}劇場{\c&H060200&}之二
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:22.66,SignC,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26}{\1c&H9D81FF&}小{\1c&H59B9FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}劇場{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HC4C700&\b1\bord6}②{\1c&H775DFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}自{\1c&HD097A8&\3c&HFFFFFF&}稱{\1c&HCFD000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}老師{\1c&H9D81FF&}、{\1c&H59B9FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}碧{\1c&HD097A8&\3c&HFFFFFF&}翠{\1c&HCFD000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}絲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:20.52,Top,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的那兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.52,0:00:23.29,Top,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,你們吵吵鬧鬧的打擾到上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:24.89,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,快點回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.89,0:00:26.86,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,你看 這就來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.86,0:00:28.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,呃 誰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.05,0:00:29.31,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,那位男性
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.31,0:00:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快閉上你的嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.69,0:00:33.09,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂碧翠子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡在設定上可是學校哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.06,0:00:37.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,不是小孩子該來的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.36,0:00:40.05,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.05,0:00:42.64,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小哥 你還是快點道歉會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.05,0:00:43.21,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你先是跟我說話 然後還把我抱了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.05,0:00:40.05,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You talk down to me, then pick me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:43.97,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.21,0:00:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你知道你的行為是多麼可怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.21,0:00:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What terrible manners!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.97,0:00:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做的事就和平時做的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:49.21,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,對老師要放尊重一些
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.21,0:00:51.55,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,等等 碧翠子你剛剛說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.55,0:00:54.15,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,我說你一點都不懂禮儀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:56.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個 你剛剛說自己是老師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:01:01.59,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 你對碧翠絲老師我有什麼想說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.59,0:01:03.29,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,比起有什麼想說的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全是有一大堆想說的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.97,0:01:06.89,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,非要只說一個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.40,0:01:08.41,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼看都是小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.41,0:01:10.25,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,這種事想想就算了 不能說出口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:14.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,退一百步 菲魯特是同級生也就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.18,0:01:15.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,碧翠子居然是老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:17.27,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇 我說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.27,0:01:17.81,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.53,0:01:21.11,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,和老師吵架會遭遇什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.11,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我來告訴你吧嘿嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.74,0:01:25.51,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 老師我可沒做錯事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.51,0:01:27.00,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,這手勢是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.00,0:01:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:29.94,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只會懲罰這位男性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.18,0:01:33.42,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.42,0:01:35.07,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,小哥 要堅強地活下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:36.15,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,菲魯特你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.15,0:01:37.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,等等 有話好說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.67,0:01:39.58,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 已不會再原諒你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.58,0:01:42.42,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,住手住手不要再吸走魔力了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.36,0:01:49.55,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,出 出現了 碧翠絲老師的必殺搔癢攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.61,0:01:53.15,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,哼 學到教訓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.15,0:01:54.76,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,居然是搔癢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:57.65,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為又會被吸走魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:02:00.28,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,魔 魔力 你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.28,0:02:02.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,欸 就是魔力啊魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.58,0:02:05.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為一定會被你吸乾魔力來著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:08.00,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,把魔力吸乾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:10.12,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,這可真是粗俗的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:12.13,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,貝蒂是絕對不會做那種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.13,0:02:14.79,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,是啊小哥 那種事是絕不可能發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.79,0:02:15.46,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:18.26,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然明白你想被那麼做的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論怎麼說魔力都應該是佐料
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:20.55,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,唔?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:24.60,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,一提到魔力就很想吃了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:25.42,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,蛤？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:28.68,Default,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,特別是加入炸雞上簡直是人間美味
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.68,0:02:30.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 那個大概是美乃滋
